== 行車路線 ==
該線為北區歷史悠久路線之一，當時為服務多個地區乘客，其路線因而比較迂迴。該線主要途經[[粉嶺|粉嶺]]、[[大窩西支路|大窩西支路]]、[[大埔_(香港)|大埔]]、[[大埔公路|大埔公路]]、[[沙田_(香港)|沙田]]、[[獅子山隧道|獅子山隧道]]、[[九龍塘|九龍塘]]、[[油麻地|油麻地]]，並設有多個分段收費。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.681busterminal.com/70.html |title=KMB Route 九巴路線 - 70 |accessdate=2007-07-23 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604111533/http://www.681busterminal.com/70.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.i-busnet.com/busroute/kmb/kmbr70.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-07-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070706065253/http://www.i-busnet.com/busroute/kmb/kmbr70.html |archivedate=2007-07-06 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stopreporter.com/index.php?click=kmbsearch.php&route=70&company=kmb |title=Stopreporter<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2007-07-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220855/http://www.stopreporter.com/index.php?click=kmbsearch.php&route=70&company=kmb |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

